                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Description:</strong> Retrieve a list of all posts.</p>
                    <div class="bg-secondary text-light p-3 rounded mt-3">
                      <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
                      <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-2 rounded"><code>GET /http://localhost:3000/api/posts</code></pre>
