                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Description:</strong> Retrieve a single post by its ID.</p>
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Parameters:</strong></p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                      <li><strong>id</strong> (string): The ID of the post.</li>
