                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                      <li><strong>title</strong> (string): The new title of the post.</li>
                      <li><strong>content</strong> (string): The new content of the post.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="bg-secondary text-light p-3 rounded mt-3">
                      <p><strong>Example Request:</strong></p>
                      <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-2 rounded"><code>PUT http://localhost:3000/api/posts/1
          {
            "title": "Updated Post",
            "content": "This is the updated content."
          }</code></pre>
